u064e\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u062b\u064e\u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064b\u0627","numberInSurah":27,"juz":29},{"number":5619,"text":"\u0646\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0646\u064f \u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0634\u064e\u062f\u064e\u062f\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u06d6 \u0648\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0634\u0650\u0626\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0628\u064e\u062f\u0651\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u062a\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064b\u0627","numberInSurah":28,"juz":29},{"number":5620,"text":"\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0647\u064e\u0670\u0630\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u062a\u064e\u0630\u0652\u0643\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064c \u06d6 \u0641\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u062a\u0651\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0630\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649\u0670 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0651\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064b\u0627","numberInSurah":29,"juz":29},{"number":5621,"text":"\u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u06da \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064b\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0643\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064b\u0627","numberInSurah":30,"juz":29},{"number":5622,"text":"\u064a\u064f\u062f\u0652\u062e\u0650\u0644\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062a\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u06da \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0638\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062f\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064b\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064b\u0627","numberInSurah":31,"juz":29}],"edition":{"identifier":"quran-simple","language":"ar","name":"Simple","englishName":"Simple","format":"text","type":"quran"}},{"number":76,"name":"\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0646\u0633\u0627\u0646","englishName":"Al-Insaan","englishNameTranslation":"Man","revelationType":"Medinan","numberOfAyahs":31,"ayahs":[{"text":"In the name of God, The Most Gracious, The Dispenser of Grace:"},{"number":5592,"text":"HAS THERE [not] been an endless span of time before man [appeared - a time] when he was not yet a thing to be thought of?","numberInSurah":1,"juz":29},{"number":5593,"text":"Verily, it is We who have created man out of a drop of sperm intermingled, so that We might try him [in his later life]: and therefore We made him a being endowed with hearing and sight.","numberInSurah":2,"juz":29},{"number":5594,"text":"Verily, We have shown him the way: [and it rests with him to prove himself] either grateful or ungrateful.","numberInSurah":3,"juz":29},{"number":5595,"text":"[Now,] behold, for those who deny the truth We have readied chains and shackles, and a blazing flame","numberInSurah":4,"juz":29},{"number":5596,"text":"[whereas,] behold, the truly virtuous shall drink from a cup flavoured with the calyx of sweet-smelling flowers:","numberInSurah":5,"juz":29},{"number":5597,"text":"a source [of bliss] whereof God's servants shall drink, seeing it flow in a flow abundant.","numberInSurah":6,"juz":29},{"number":5598,"text":"[The truly virtuous are] they [who] fulfil their vows, and stand in awe of a Day the woe of which is bound to spread far and wide,","numberInSurah":7,"juz":29},{"number":5599,"text":"and who give food - however great be their own want of it - unto the needy, and the orphan, and the captive,","numberInSurah":8,"juz":29},{"number":5600,"text":"[saying, in their hearts,] \"We feed you for the sake of God alone: we desire no recompense from you, nor thanks:","numberInSurah":9,"juz":29},{"number":5601,"text":"behold, we stand in awe of our Sustainer's judgment on a distressful, fateful Day!\"","numberInSurah":10,"juz":29},{"number":5602,"text":"And so, God will preserve them from the woes of that Day, and will bestow on them brightness and joy,","numberInSurah":11,"juz":29},{"number":5603,"text":"and will reward them for all their patience in adversity with a garden [of bliss] and with [garments of] silk.","numberInSurah":12,"juz":29},{"number":5604,"text":"In that [garden] they will on couches recline, and will know therein neither [burning] sun nor cold severe,","numberInSurah":13,"juz":29},{"number":5605,"text":"since its [blissful] shades will come down low over them, and low will hang down its clusters of fruit, most easy to reach.","numberInSurah":14,"juz":29},{"number":5606,"text":"And they will be waited upon with vessels of silver and goblets that will [seem to] be crystal \u2013","numberInSurah":15,"juz":29},{"number":5607,"text":"crystal-like, [but] of silver - the measure whereof they alone will determine.","numberInSurah":16,"juz":29},{"number":5608,"text":"And in that [paradise] they will be given to drink of a cup flavoured with ginger,","numberInSurah":17,"juz":29},{"number":5609,"text":"[derived from] a source [to be found] therein, whose name is \"Seek Thy Way\".","numberInSurah":18,"juz":29},{"number":5610,"text":"And immortal youths will wait upon them: when thou seest them, thou wouldst deem them to be scattered pearls;","numberInSurah":19,"juz":29},{"number":5611,"text":"and when thou seest [anything that is] there thou wilt see [only] bliss and a realm transcendent","numberInSurah":20,"juz":29},{"number":5612,"text":"Upon those [blest] will be garments of green silk and brocade; and they will be adorned with bracelets of silver. And their Sustainer will them to drink of a drink most pure.","numberInSurah":21,"juz":29},{"number":5613,"text":"[And they will be told:] \"Verily, all this is your reward since Your endeavour [in life] has met [God's] goodly acceptance!\"","numberInSurah":22,"juz":29},{"number":5614,"text":"VERILY, [O believer,] it is We who have bestowed from on high this Qur\u2019an upon thee, step by step - truly a bestowal from on high!","numberInSurah":23,"juz":29},{"number":5615,"text":"Await, then, in all patience thy Sustainer's judgment, and pay no heed to any of them, who is a wilful sinner or an ingrate;","numberInSurah":24,"juz":29},{"number":5616,"text":"and bear in mind thy Sustainer's name at morn and evening","numberInSurah":25,"juz":29},{"number":5617,"text":"and during some of the night, and prostrate thyself before Him, and extol His limitless glory throughout the long night.","numberInSurah":26,"juz":29},{"number":5618,"text":"Behold, they [who are unmindful of God] love this fleeting life, and leave behind them [all thought of] a grief-laden Day.","numberInSurah":27,"juz":29},{"number":5619,"text":"[They will not admit to themselves that] it We who have created them and strengthened their make - and [that] if it be Our will We can replace them entirely with others of their kind.","numberInSurah":28,"juz":29},{"number":5620,"text":"VERILY, all this is an admonition: whoever, then, so wills, may unto his Sustainer find a way.","numberInSurah":29,"juz":29},{"number":5621,"text":"But you cannot will it unless God wills [to show you that way]: for, behold, God is indeed all-seeing, wise.","numberInSurah":30,"juz":29},{"number":5622,"text":"He admits unto His grace everyone who wills [to be admitted]; but as for the evildoers - for them has He readied grievous suffering [in the life to come].","numberInSurah":31,"juz":29}],"edition":{"identifier":"en.asad","language":"en","name":"Asad","englishName":"Muhammad Asad","format":"text","type":"translation"}}]}